# Poiseuille flow driven by body force
# Validation: parabolic profile ux(y) = Fx/(2*nu) * y * (Ly - y)

Simulation poiseuille D2Q9
Domain  L = 0.125 x 1.0  N = 4 x 32
Physics nu = 0.1  Fx = 1e-5

Boundary x periodic
Boundary south wall
Boundary north wall

Run 10000 steps
Output vtk every 2000 [rho, ux, uy]
